observationText: The COLO 668 cell line was used to develop a cisplatin-resistant subline called SNU-668-CIS.
The COLO 668 cell line was also used to develop a 5-fluorouracil-resistant subline called SNU-668-5FU.
The COLO 668 cell line was further used to develop a doxorubicin-resistant subline called SNU-668-DOX.
